fields.name: Fizzy Worms
fields.description:
Tasty , zingy worms ..super tasty raspberry sour , flavoured worms. 
** no worms were harmed in the making of these treats ;)

fields.name: jelly beans
fields.description: An assortment of flavours and colours, these sweet candys covered in a soft and chew shell with a soft , jelly inside. Sweet Moments are one of the few companies to supply a vegan jellybean treat. Get em while they last !!!

fields.name: Mallow Hearts
fields.description: A perfect gift for a loved one...or better yet, for you! Soft , powdered , puffs of joy! These little squishy snacks are  great for a treat, and bonus theres only 25 CALORIES per mallow. Hows that for your sweet moment

fields.name: Wine Gums
fields.description: An oldie but a goodie. These old style treats never go out of style. With our new and improved vegan recipe you can now enjoy these old boys. Our wine gums come in a range of flavours.

fields.name: Butterscotch Candies
fields.description: Remember these?? Of course you do...but not like this. These old school hard candies are the first of their kind. Never before seen, Vegan Butterscotch! Here at sweet Moments we like to deliver the unbelievable, so why not be on the receiving end aye?

fields.name: Coconut Milk Chocolate
fields.description: Tis our yummy chocolate invention. Made with coconut milk and mixed with little tiny mallows.

fields.name: Fizzy Hearts
fields.description: Our little fizzy hearts are a zesty sherbert flavour that come with their own little love message to you!

fields.name: Sour candied fruit jellies
fields.description: Yummy candied fruit. caramalized and tossed in sugar, these little guys come with a legitimate fruity flavour and tons of sour sugar to make your eyes water

fields.name: sour jellyworms
fields.description: eyewateringly sour. These little guys are for the brave...or those who have no tastebuds. Raspberry and blueberry flavoured.

fields.name: Chocolate Sprinkled bites
fields.description: Bite size , creamy , white chocolate hearts. Made with plant based milk.

fields.name: Salted Carmel Fudge
fields.description: The best of its vegan kind! This salty sweet fudge melts in your mouth. Made with sea salt and fudgey goodness
